<subSubSection id="C3266556D364FFC3FF17FA8ADB15FA61" pageId="7" pageNumber="488" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8336DDD364FFC3FF17FA8ADB15FA61" blockId="7.[151,1437,541,1432]" pageId="7" pageNumber="488">
<emphasis id="B948EACFD364FFC3FF17FA8ADF74FA85" bold="true" box="[199,315,1369,1395]" pageId="7" pageNumber="488">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C3C4D5ED364FFC3FE92FA8ADFA1FA85" authorityName="Bayarsaikhan &amp; Bae" authorityYear="2015" box="[322,494,1369,1395]" class="Insecta" family="Erebidae" genus="Stictane" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cambodensis">
<emphasis id="B948EACFD364FFC3FE92FA8ADFA1FA85" box="[322,494,1369,1395]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="488">S. cambodensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described for males by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAD4B2CD364FFC3FCF9FA8ADA2BFA82" author="Bayarsaikhan, U. &amp; Bae, Y. S." box="[809,1124,1369,1396]" pageId="7" pageNumber="488" pagination="241 - 252" refId="ref6065" refString="Bayarsaikhan, U. &amp; Bae, Y. S. (2015) Three new species of Stictane Hampson, 1900 (Erebidae, Arctiinae) from Cambodia, with checklist of Stictane. Zootaxa, 3981 (2), 241 - 252. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3981.2.5" type="journal article" year="2015">Bayarsaikhan &amp; Bae (2015)</bibRefCitation>
. In this study, this species is newly recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="F32B764DD364FFC3FE58FAAEDFA3FA61" box="[392,492,1405,1431]" name="Thailand" pageId="7" pageNumber="488">Thailand</collectingCountry>
(Nakhon Si Tammarat province), and its female is described for the first time.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
